text.tspan: 1) Import artwork and move it below cabinet-artwork-right
in the Layers and Objects dialog
2) Hide the original cabinet-artwork-right by selecting it
in the Layers and Objects Dialog and click the eye
3) Resize and reposition your artwork to fit over mask
4) Select cabinet-mask-right and your new cabinet-artwork-right
layer in the Layers and Objects dialog
5) Enable the cabinet-black-background-right if the artwork
doesn't fully fit inside the mask
6) Select Object menu -> Clip -> Set Clip
7) Export clipped image as a png file at 300dpi
